****************************************************************************
* 			Deprecated functions				   *
****************************************************************************

QApplication::setColorMode() and colorMode() will be obsoleted. Use
setColorSpec() and colorSpec() instead.

****************************************************************************
* 			     New classes				   *
****************************************************************************

QSlider is a range input widget. If you have been using a standalone
QScrollBar, you will probably want to switch to a QSlider.

QSpinBox provides a spin box, sometimes called up-down widget, little
arrows widget or spin button.


